according to the 230 million plan by the nonprofit foundation for 
community development 
the highest building in soweto where an estimated 25 million 
people live on 40 square miles of low hills is now a 10story 
nurses dormitory 
aside from a few twostory houses in higherincome 
neighborhoods sowetans live on small lots in onestory houses 
many have outside toilets and no bathrooms 
